long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension features the ability to categorize the visited website history based on search keywords made on Google. As users, we often visit numerous websites through Google for tasks, studies, work, and may have multiple internet windows open at once. "Hey Googler - 키워드에 따른 구글링 기록 분류" allows us to easily close these internet windows, ensuring a pleasant search environment and optimizing memory usage.
